{
  "stem": "6052.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because what happens-- in this time, I was at Hachshara, that my brother and my sister and my mother were forced, under the new rules, to deliver all their [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] valuables, all their jewelry, what they had.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had-- we had some.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had many, because we were wealthy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the radio.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We could not listen any more to radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jews were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And how it should be delivered and when delivered.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And later on, there was a story that they-- not a story, it was a fact.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They came to our apartment and raided it in order to find something which was not delivered.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know how all these things came about.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I just read, later on, when a protocol was made and when my brother related these things to a lawyer to try to tell them, this you took from us, this we want back.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We did not succeed much.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "This was-- When we succeeded in something very symbolic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But all this was then later made like it-- it was not so.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was in such confusing ways.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They said we-- they took it because a German law demanded it that we give it to them, because it was kind of penalty put on all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Something to that effect.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "How exactly, I cannot formulate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Not at this time, I could never formulate it, because I did not have all the documentation.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But from what I read, it was that it simply was taken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "What-- when we left-- my brother and I-- when we left with this small group of 16, which I will come about soon to tell, then we had nothing.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We left without anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
